spells.description:
Use: Channel to vent flames for 2 sec, dealing 3.3 million Fire damage split between all nearby enemies.

Mechanical enemies become Superheated, taking 159,293  additional Fire damage when struck by your next harmful ability. (2 Min Cooldown)

Use: Become Mudborne, absorbing 10.8 million damage and pulsing 534,340 Nature damage split between nearby enemies over 10 sec.

Periodic damage you take coalesces into pungent mud to feed the ritual, reducing this cooldown by 2.0 sec. (2 Min Cooldown)
Equip: Being one of the devout grants an additional 261 Agility.
